# zice-agent

- **Port 8081.** Platform data only via `internal/client` zice-core HTTP client — not direct SQL on core tables.
- Agent-owned tables only in `sql/migrations/`; apply with platform `make db-migrate-agent`.
- New tools: implement in `internal/tools/`, register in router setup; use service key for core calls.
- Chat uses SSE; match zice-core response patterns for non-stream JSON.
- Rate limits and org middleware are required on protected routes — do not skip `RequireOrg`.

Repo `AGENTS.md` (after `make sync-agent-docs`) documents env vars and layout.
